OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry with variable cloud
OL,6,Famounts. Some sunny spells are likely,
OL,7,Fwith temperatures near normal for
OL,8,FMarch, however the breeze will lead to
OL,9,Fit feeling cooler. Although the odd
OL,10,Fshower cannot be ruled out.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud thickening through the
OL,13,Fevening and overnight, but all parts
OL,14,Flikely staying dry. Winds also
OL,15,Fgradually strengthening, and turning
OL,16,Fgusty by dawn. Likely staying frost
OL,17,Ffree.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
