OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA cloudy but dry start, but
OL,6,Fsome outbreaks of rain possible by
OL,7,Fmidday. These continuing on and off
OL,8,Fthrough the afternoon, before heavier
OL,9,Fand blustery rain moves through
OL,10,Fovernight. Windy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold and
OL,13,Fbreezy Friday with brighter spell and
OL,14,Foccasional showers. Less cold
OL,15,FSaturday, but still the odd shower
OL,16,Flikely. Further rain and strong winds
OL,17,Fspreading east Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
